Faye Grant https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Faye_Grant 0 Faye Grant (born Faye Elizabeth Yoe, July 16, 1957) is an American film, television and stage actress. She is best known for her role as Julie Parrish in NBC's science fiction series, V, between 1983 and 1985.
